---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Instant Personal Loan - Disbursal in 2 Hours | TrueCred Loan Expert">

<!-- Page Hero -->
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="breadcrumb">
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <span class="sep"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i></span>
        <a href="#">Loans</a>
        <span class="sep"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i></span>
        <span>Instant Personal Loan</span>
      </div>
      <h1>Instant Personal Loan</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">Need money urgently? Get an instant personal loan with disbursal in as fast as 2 hours. 100% digital application process with minimal documentation and instant approval. Available 24/7 through our partner fintech lenders.</p>
      <div class="hero-highlights">
        <div class="highlight-item">
          <i class="fas fa-bolt"></i>
          <span>Disbursal: As Fast as 2 Hours</span>
        </div>
        <div class="highlight-item">
          <i class="fas fa-indian-rupee-sign"></i>
          <span>Loan Amount: ₹10K - ₹25L</span>
        </div>
        <div class="highlight-item">
          <i class="fas fa-percent"></i>
          <span>Interest: 10.49% onwards</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Page Content -->
  <section class="page-content">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content-grid">

        <!-- Main Content -->
        <div class="content-main">
          <h2>What is an Instant Personal Loan?</h2>
          <p>An instant personal loan is a fully digital, quick-disbursal loan that gets credited to your bank account within minutes to a few hours of approval. Unlike traditional personal loans that take 3-7 days, instant loans leverage AI-based credit assessment, Aadhaar e-KYC, and automated underwriting to process applications in real-time. These loans are ideal for medical emergencies, urgent travel, last-minute bill payments, or any situation where you need funds immediately.</p>
          <p>TrueCred partners with leading digital lenders like Bajaj Finserv, MoneyTap, KreditBee, Fi Money, and others who specialize in instant loan disbursal. Our platform lets you compare rates, check real-time eligibility, and apply from your phone — all in under 5 minutes. With loan amounts ranging from ₹10,000 to ₹25,00,000, you can find the right instant loan for any need, any time of the day.</p>

          <div class="info-grid">
            <div class="info-box">
              <span class="info-value">2 Hrs</span>
              <span class="info-label">Fastest Disbursal</span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-box">
              <span class="info-value">₹25 Lakh</span>
              <span class="info-label">Max Loan Amount</span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-box">
              <span class="info-value">100%</span>
              <span class="info-label">Digital Process</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <h3>Instant Personal Loan Interest Rates — April 2026</h3>
          <table class="rate-table">
            <thead>
              <tr>
                <th>Bank / NBFC</th>
                <th>Interest Rate (p.a.)</th>
                <th>Processing Fee</th>
                <th>Max Tenure</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr>
                <td>Bajaj Finserv</td>
                <td>10.49% onwards</td>
                <td>Up to 2.50%</td>
                <td>5 Years</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>ICICI Bank</td>
                <td>10.99% onwards</td>
                <td>Up to 2.25%</td>
                <td>5 Years</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>MoneyTap</td>
                <td>13.00% onwards</td>
                <td>Up to 2.00%</td>
                <td>3 Years</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>KreditBee</td>
                <td>14.00% onwards</td>
                <td>Up to 3.00%</td>
                <td>2 Years</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>Fi Money</td>
                <td>12.50% onwards</td>
                <td>Up to 2.50%</td>
                <td>3 Years</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>

          <h3>Eligibility Criteria</h3>
          <ul class="feature-list">
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> Indian citizen aged between 21 and 57 years</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> Minimum monthly income of ₹15,000 (salaried) or ₹20,000 (self-employed)</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> CIBIL score of 680 or above for instant approval</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> Active bank account with at least 6 months of transaction history</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> Smartphone with internet access for digital KYC and verification</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> Valid Aadhaar and PAN card linked to mobile number</li>
          </ul>

          <h3>How to Get an Instant Personal Loan</h3>
          <div class="steps-grid">
            <div class="step-card">
              <div class="step-num">1</div>
              <h4>Quick Application</h4>
              <p>Fill in basic details — name, income, PAN, and loan amount — in under 2 minutes on our mobile-friendly platform.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step-card">
              <div class="step-num">2</div>
              <h4>Instant Eligibility</h4>
              <p>Our AI engine checks your eligibility across 30+ instant lenders simultaneously and shows approved offers in seconds.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step-card">
              <div class="step-num">3</div>
              <h4>Digital KYC</h4>
              <p>Complete Aadhaar-based e-KYC with OTP verification. No branch visits, no physical documents, no waiting.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step-card">
              <div class="step-num">4</div>
              <h4>Money in Account</h4>
              <p>Accept the best offer and receive the loan amount in your bank account within 2 hours. Use it for anything you need.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <h3>Documents Required</h3>
          <ul class="feature-list">
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> PAN Card — for identity verification and credit check</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> Aadhaar Card — for e-KYC verification via OTP</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> Selfie verification — live photo for face match with Aadhaar</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> Bank statement (digital) — auto-fetched via Account Aggregator or net banking</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> Salary slip not required for most instant loan applications</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> No physical documents — entire process is paperless</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Sidebar -->
        <div class="content-sidebar">
          <div class="sidebar-card">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-file-signature"></i> Get Instant Loan Now</h3>
            <form class="sidebar-form" onsubmit="return false;">
              <div class="form-group">
                <input type="text" class="form-input" placeholder="Full Name" required>
              </div>
              <div class="form-group">
                <input type="tel" class="form-input" placeholder="Mobile Number" maxlength="10" required>
              </div>
              <div class="form-group">
                <select class="form-input" required>
                  <option value="" disabled selected>Loan Amount</option>
                  <option value="10000">₹10,000</option>
                  <option value="25000">₹25,000</option>
                  <option value="50000">₹50,000</option>
                  <option value="100000">₹1,00,000</option>
                  <option value="200000">₹2,00,000</option>
                  <option value="500000">₹5,00,000</option>
                  <option value="1000000">₹10,00,000</option>
                  <option value="1500000">₹15,00,000</option>
                  <option value="2500000">₹25,00,000</option>
                </select>
              </div>
              <div class="form-group">
                <input type="text" class="form-input" placeholder="City" required>
              </div>
              <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-block" style="width:100%;justify-content:center;">
                Apply Now <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i>
              </button>
            </form>
          </div>

          <div class="sidebar-card">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-link"></i> Quick Links</h3>
            <div class="sidebar-links">
              <a href="/pages/business-loan"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> Business Loan</a>
              <a href="/pages/home-loan"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> Home Loan</a>
              <a href="/pages/loan-against-property"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> Loan Against Property</a>
              <a href="/pages/gold-loan"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> Gold Loan</a>
              <a href="/pages/education-loan"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> Education Loan</a>
              <a href="/pages/car-loan"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> Car Loan</a>
              <a href="/pages/credit-cards"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> Credit Cards</a>
              <a href="/pages/credit-score"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> Credit Score</a>
              <a href="/pages/calculators"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> EMI Calculator</a>
              <a href="/pages/insurance"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> Insurance</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section class="faq-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-tag">Got Questions?</span>
        <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <p>Common questions about instant personal loans.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-list">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question">
            How fast can I get an instant personal loan?
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">
              The fastest instant personal loans on TrueCred can be disbursed within 2 hours of application. For pre-approved customers, some lenders disburse within 10-15 minutes. The timeline depends on the lender, your profile, and how quickly you complete the e-KYC process. Most applications are processed within 2-4 hours during business hours.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question">
            Are instant personal loans safe?
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">
              Yes, instant loans from TrueCred's partner lenders are completely safe. All our partners are RBI-registered banks, NBFCs, or lending platforms that comply with regulatory guidelines. Your data is encrypted and protected under strict privacy policies. Always verify the lender's RBI registration and avoid any lender not listed on regulated platforms.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question">
            What is the maximum amount I can get as an instant loan?
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">
              Instant personal loan amounts on TrueCred range from ₹10,000 to ₹25,00,000 depending on the lender and your profile. First-time borrowers may receive lower amounts (₹10,000 to ₹2,00,000), while existing customers with good repayment history can access up to ₹25 lakhs. Your income, credit score, and employer category determine the final sanctioned amount.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question">
            Can I get an instant loan on weekends or holidays?
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">
              Yes, most fintech lenders on TrueCred process instant loan applications 24/7, including weekends and holidays. The application, verification, and approval happen digitally round the clock. However, actual bank transfers may depend on banking hours — NEFT/RTGS transfers may be delayed outside banking hours, but UPI and IMPS transfers work 24/7.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question">
            What happens if my instant loan application is rejected?
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">
              If your application is rejected by one lender, TrueCred automatically matches you with alternative lenders who may approve your profile. Common reasons for rejection include low CIBIL score, insufficient income, high existing debt, or incomplete KYC. You can improve your chances by fixing the rejection reason and reapplying after 30 days.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Page CTA -->
  <section class="page-content" style="padding-top:0;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="page-cta">
        <div>
          <h3>Get Instant Funds When You Need Them Most</h3>
          <p>Apply in 2 minutes, get approved instantly, and receive money in your bank within 2 hours.</p>
        </div>
        <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline" style="color:#fff;border:2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.5);padding:14px 32px;font-size:0.95rem;">
          Apply Now <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer -->

</BaseLayout>
